\f0\b \cb3 Class name: 
\f1\b0 MapNode\cb1 \

\f0\b \cb3 Purpose and description of class:\

\f1\b0 \cb1 The MapNode class consists of a location, name, list of MapEdges, and list of neighbor MapNodes, and the methods associated with adding and accessing the data stored within.  This allowed me to represent a geographical location as a MapNode with associated neighbors and roads.\
\
