\f0\b \cb3 Class name: 
\f1\b0 MapEdge\cb1 \

\f0\b \cb3 Purpose and description of class:\

\f1\b0 \cf4 \cb5 The MapEdge class consists of a start and end location, distance between the two, and a road name and type.  The purpose is to represent the roads between MapNodes (geographic points) on the map.\cf2 \cb1 \
\

